description: Jake is a 19 year old skater who we came across on our way to lunch outside of our office.There were a bunch of us together and one of the girls casually walked up to him and asked him if he wanted to stop by for a shoot. Jake said he was interested and when he met with us the next day, all he could talk about was girls and sex.Well, with that kind of sexual energy, we knew he'd be great. And with that, we are proud to bring you Jake.Enjoy him as he enjoys himself.
title: Jake
